#. App name - 50 chars limit
#: descriptions/google-play.html%2Bhtml.body.h3:5-1
msgid "Collabora Office: LibreOffice, OpenOffice & more"
msgstr "Collabora Office: LibreOffice, OpenOffice med mere"

#. Short description - 80 chars limit
#: descriptions/google-play.html%2Bhtml.body.p:9-1
msgid ""
"LibreOffice based editor for Microsoft Office, LibreOffice and OpenOffice "
"docs."
msgstr "LibreOffice baseret editor til Microsoft Office og OpenOffice docs."

#. Long description
#: descriptions/google-play.html%2Bhtml.body.p:13-1
msgid ""
"Collabora Office is a text editor, spreadsheet and presentation program "
"based on LibreOffice, the world's most popular Open Source office suite - "
"and now it's on Android, enhancing your possibilities to work on mobile and "
"for collaboration."
msgstr ""
"Collabora Office er et tekstredigerings-, regnearks- og præsentationsprogram "
"baseret på LibreOffice, verdens mest populære Open Source office-pakke – "
"findes nu på Android, hvilket forbedrer dine muligheder for at arbejde på "
"mobilen og for samarbejde."

#. Long description
#: descriptions/google-play.html%2Bhtml.body.p:17-1
msgid ""
"This app is in active development, feedback and bug reports are very welcome."
msgstr ""
"Denne app er under fortsat udvikling. Feedback og fejlrapporter er meget "
"velkomne."

#. Long description
#: descriptions/google-play.html%2Bhtml.body.p:21-1
msgid "Supported files:"
msgstr "Understøttede filer:"

#: descriptions/google-play.html%2Bhtml.body.ul.li:26-5
msgid "Open Document Format (.odt, .odp, .ods, .ots, .ott, .otp)"
msgstr "Åbn dokumentformat (.odt, .odp, .ods, .ots, .ott, .otp)"

#: descriptions/google-play.html%2Bhtml.body.ul.li:27-5
msgid ""
"Microsoft Office 2007/2010/2013/2016/2019 "
"(.docx, .pptx, .xlsx, .dotx, .xltx, .ppsx)"
msgstr ""
"Microsoft Office 2007/2010/2013/2016/2019 "
"(.docx, .pptx, .xlsx, .dotx, .xltx, .ppsx)"

#: descriptions/google-play.html%2Bhtml.body.ul.li:28-5
msgid "Microsoft Office 97/2000/XP/2003 (.doc, .ppt, .xls, .dot, .xlt, .pps)"
msgstr "Microsoft Office 97/2000/XP/2003 (.doc, .ppt, .xls, .dot, .xlt, .pps)"

#. Long description
#: descriptions/google-play.html%2Bhtml.body.p:31-1
msgid "Report issues:"
msgstr "Rapporter problemer:"

#. Long description
#: descriptions/google-play.html%2Bhtml.body.p:35-1
msgid ""
"Use the bugtracker and attach any files that caused problems via <a "
"href=\"https://col.la/android\"> https://col.la/android</a>. Please note "
"that anything you enter in the bugtracker will be public."
msgstr ""
"Brug fejlsøgeren og vedhæft de filer, der forårsagede problemer, gennem <a "
"href=\"https://col.la/android\"> https://col.la/android</a>. Bemærk "
"venligst, at dét, du skriver i fejlsøgeren, vil være synligt for "
"offentligheden."

#. Long description
#: descriptions/google-play.html%2Bhtml.body.p:40-1
msgid "About the app:"
msgstr "Om appen:"

#. Long description
#: descriptions/google-play.html%2Bhtml.body.p:44-1
msgid ""
"Collabora Office for Android uses the same engine as LibreOffice for "
"Windows, Mac, and Linux. This, combined with a new front-end based on "
"Collabora Online, reads and saves documents similarly to LibreOffice desktop."
msgstr ""
"Collabora Office til Android bruger den samme motor som LibreOffice til "
"Windows, Mac, og Linux. Dette, kombineret med en ny grafisk brugerflade "
"baseret på Collabora Online, indlæser og gemmer dokumenter på samme måde som "
"LibreOffice på en computer."

#. Long description
#: descriptions/google-play.html%2Bhtml.body.p:48-1
msgid ""
"Collabora Engineers Tor Lillqvist, Tomaž Vajngerl, Michael Meeks, Miklos "
"Vajna, Jan Holešovský, Mert Tümer, Rashesh Padia and Skyler Grey have been "
"developing Android support since 2012, with the help of Google Summer of "
"Code students Andrzej Hunt, Iain Billet and Kaishu Sahu."
msgstr ""
"Collabora-ingeniørerne Tor Lillqvist, Tomaž Vajngerl, Michael Meeks, Miklos "
"Vajna, Jan Holešovský, Mert Tümer, Rashesh Padia og Skyler Grey har udviklet "
"på Android-understøttelse siden 2012 med hjælp fra Google Summer of Code-"
"studenterne Andrzej Hunt, Iain Billet og Kaishu Sahu."

